  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency semver to v5.5.0 - autoclosed",
  "body": "This Pull Request updates dependency [semver](https://github.com/npm/node-semver) from `v5.4.1` to `v5.5.0`\n\n**Note**: This PR was created on a configured schedule (\"every weekend\" in timezone `Europe/Paris`) and will not receive updates outside those times.\n\n\n\n<details>\n<summary>Commits</summary>\n\n#### v5.5.0\n-   [`7184ff4`](https://github.com/npm/node-semver/commit/7184ff429eaf6a969b292d4129e4fffeb666031d) range.bnf: Remove unnecessary empty entry\n-   [`906b664`](https://github.com/npm/node-semver/commit/906b6641c5b82ceaaa60e94bf1f1cc59f4a4aa8f) travis: don&#x27;t cache node_modules\n-   [`ec6f97a`](https://github.com/npm/node-semver/commit/ec6f97ad9bb4e8ffe9100c2f331f4e0015a24212) range.bnf: Fix invalid bracket expression\n-   [`68cef2d`](https://github.com/npm/node-semver/commit/68cef2d74d4c6fcb76b5dd2d20231b2f3f9c78ac) Added version coercion to the module and CLI.\n-   [`e7092b4`](https://github.com/npm/node-semver/commit/e7092b4040360f1b24c1119defe45ed3b38a77ef) Improved coerce regex and added coerce to README.\n-   [`1d37529`](https://github.com/npm/node-semver/commit/1d37529091c09b17396ef21d86e9617e163e763f) Cleaned up coerce behavior\n-   [`44cbc84`](https://github.com/npm/node-semver/commit/44cbc8482ac4f0f8d2de0abb7f8808056d2d55f9) v5.5.0\n\n</details>\n\n\n\n---\n\nThis PR has been generated by [Renovate Bot](https://renovateapp.com).",
